This is another episode of BBC's Hustler. A great show if you want it but not The Strangers as Anonymous claims.

Download 0.1% of the file and open it in GOM or VLC and you see what it is. If it gives a file in use error, stop the torrent, try again. Other way to do it too but I think I'll find some time over the long weekend to make a forum post I can link to. If not then I'll do it soon.
